# 🖼️ Application Screenshots & Visuals
This directory contains UI mockups, architecture diagrams, and system flowcharts.

## 📱 Dashboard Overview (Planned)
- **Top Bar:** Institution branding and system health.
- **Left Panel:** Student directory with risk flags (Green/Amber/Red).
- **Center Panel:** Predictive insights, grade bands, and SHAP feature influence.
- **Right Panel:** Recommended intervention workflow (e.g., "Schedule Tutoring").

